\l Le dijo dice.

\t Pongamos re tijkojchaq pongamos mentiras chuch,
\b P-o-n-g-a-mo-s re tij-ko-j-chaq po-n-g-a-mo-s me-nti-ra-s chu-ch-,
\q Ponga-mo-s re tij-ko-j-chaq po-nga-mo-s me-nti-ra-s chu-ch-,
\g 
